\vnabla\big(xy-2x+yz+x^2+y^2+z^3-7\big)\big|_{(0,2,1)}
&=\llt y-2+2x\,,\,x+z+2y\,,\,y+3z^2\rgt\big|_{(0,2,1)}\\
&=\llt 0, 5, 5\rgt
\end{align*}
So the tangent plane is 
