=\lim_{(x,y)\rightarrow(0,0)}\frac{xy}{\sin(xy)}\ 
\lim_{(x,y)\rightarrow(0,0)}\frac{\sin(xy)}{x^2+y^2}
\end{equation*}
would also exist. (Recall that $\dst\lim_{t\rightarrow 0}\tfrac{\sin t}{t}
