&=1+(1)^4=2
\end{align*}
and the second limit is nonzero,
\begin{equation*}
\lim_{(x,y)\rightarrow(-1,1)}\frac{x^2+2xy^2+y^4}{1+y^4}=\frac{0}{2}=0
\end{equation*}




