solution:
\begin{solution}
The function
\begin{align*}
u(\rho, r,\theta) &= \big[\rho r\cos\theta\big]^2 
                      +\big[\rho r\sin\theta\big] \rho r \\
&=\rho^2 r^2\cos^2\theta +\rho^2 r^2\sin\theta
