For the surface $z=f(x,y)=y^{3/2}$,
\begin{equation*}
\dee{S}=\sqrt{1+f_x^2+f_y^2}\ \dee{x}\dee{y}
=\sqrt{1+\Big(\frac{3}{2}\sqrt{y}\Big)^2}\ \dee{x}\dee{y}
=\sqrt{1+\frac{9}{4}y}\ \dee{x}\dee{y}
