z-4 = - \sqrt{\frac{x^2+y^2}{3}}
\end{equation*}
(which contains the points $(0,0,4)$ and $(\sqrt{3},0,3)$) and
is bounded on the bottom by the  cone
\begin{equation*}
z = \sqrt{3(x^2+y^2)}
\end{equation*}
(which contains the points $(0,0,0)$ and $(\sqrt{3},0,3)$).

iii. The bottom part is the Pac--Man
