\int_{-4}^0\int_{\sqrt{-y}}^2 \cos(x^3)\,\dee{x}\,\dee{y}
&=\int_0^2\dee{x}\int_{-x^2}^0\dee{y}\ \cos(x^3) \\
&=\int_0^2\dee{x}\ x^2\ \cos(x^3) 
