All together $R$ has
\begin{align*}
\text{Area}
&= \int_{-1}^2 \big[2+x-x^2\big]\ \dee{x} \\
&=\bigg[2x+\frac{x^2}{2}-\frac{x^3}{3}\bigg]_{-1}^2  \\
