I_2&=\int_0^\infty e^{-x} \cos(2x)\,\dee{x}
&&=\lim_{R\rightarrow\infty}\int_0^R e^{-x} \cos(2x)\,\dee{x} \\
&&&=\lim_{R\rightarrow\infty}
\bigg(\Big[-e^{-x}\cos(2x)\Big]_0^R-2\int_0^R e^{-x} \sin(2x)\,\dee{x}
                               \bigg)
=1-2I_1
