\begin{align*}
f'(0)&=\lim_{h \rightarrow 0} \frac{f(0+h)-f(0)}{h}\\
&=\lim_{h \rightarrow 0} \frac{h\log_{10}(2h+10)-0}{h}\\
&=\lim_{h \rightarrow 0} \log_{10}(2h+10)=\log_{10}(10)=1
