\sqrt{xy} &= x^2y-2\\
\frac{1}{2\sqrt{xy}}\cdot \diff{}{x}\{xy\}&=(2x)y+x^2\ds\diff{y}{x}\\
\frac{y+x\diff{y}{x}}{2\sqrt{xy}}&=2xy+x^2\diff{y}{x}
