y_0 +(4y_0+2)z_0 &=0 \tag{E2}
\end{align*}
The question specifies that $x_0\ne 0$, so (E1) forces $z_0=-\frac{1}{2}$.
Substituting $z_0=-\frac{1}{2}$ into (E2) gives
\begin{equation*}
